</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>【有片睇】SEGA「世界最高速」PC 時速達 100 公里搭載遙控車上</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2021/12/28/sega-pc-100/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=sega-pc-100</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Christy]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 28 Dec 2021 10:39:32 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[SEGA]]></category><category><![CDATA[SEGA Winter Sale]]></category><category><![CDATA[可行走高速 PC]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1078445</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>SEGA 現時於 Steam 平台上舉辦「SEGA Winter Sale」，並透過抽獎宣傳 SEGA 與 A [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>SEGA 現時於 Steam 平台上舉辦「SEGA Winter Sale」，並透過抽獎宣傳 SEGA 與 ATLUS 的遊戲，向玩家提供 Sonic 系列等多個遊戲優惠。中獎者更有機會獲得時速達 100 公里的可行走高速 PC 作獎品。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-28-18.36.40.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1078544 alignnone" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-28-18.36.40-594x580.jpg" alt="" width="594" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-28-18.36.40-594x580.jpg 594w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-28-18.36.40-922x900.jpg 922w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-28-18.36.40-768x750.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-28-18.36.40.jpg 1026w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 594px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-28-18.36.32.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1078543 alignnone" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-28-18.36.32-568x580.jpg" alt="" width="568" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-28-18.36.32-568x580.jpg 568w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-28-18.36.32-882x900.jpg 882w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-28-18.36.32-768x784.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-28-18.36.32.jpg 938w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 568px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/1640625651-279739e9831b29d3539e2b93add1e48b.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1078448" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/1640625651-279739e9831b29d3539e2b93add1e48b-694x364.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="364" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/1640625651-279739e9831b29d3539e2b93add1e48b-694x364.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/1640625651-279739e9831b29d3539e2b93add1e48b-768x403.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/1640625651-279739e9831b29d3539e2b93add1e48b.jpg 1000w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>是次抽獎活動為「SEGA 世界最快！可行走高速 PC」，參加者只須於 2022 年 1 月 5 日前在 Twitter 上轉載官方貼文即獲得抽獎機會，獎品包括「可行走高速 PC」及 23 款 Steam 上的 SEGA 遊戲，但只會寄送至日本國內。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="ja" dir="ltr">【セガのSteamホリデイセール記念】<br />最速ゲーミングPCを、セガが本気で創ってみました！</p><p>…なんとこのPC</p><p>最高時速 100kmで…走る！！</p><p>フォロー＆このツイートをRT！<br />抽選でセガ最速 PC＆Steamソフトをプレゼント！</p><p>↓詳細↓<a href="https://t.co/Ze1wnmBpuS">https://t.co/Ze1wnmBpuS</a><a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/%E3%82%BB%E3%82%AC%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E6%9C%80%E9%80%9FPC?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#セガ世界最速 PC</a>　<a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/%E3%82%BB%E3%82%AC%E3%82%A2%E3%83%88%E3%83%A9%E3%82%B9Steam%E3%82%BB%E3%83%BC%E3%83%AB?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#セガアトラスSteamセール</a> <a href="https://t.co/LaBeCk5q9U">pic.twitter.com/LaBeCk5q9U</a></p><p>&mdash; セガ公式アカウント🦔 (@SEGA_OFFICIAL) <a href="https://twitter.com/SEGA_OFFICIAL/status/1475391408374956033?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">December 27, 2021</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>可行走高速 PC 由 Intel 及 ASRock 贊助，並配備 Intel Core i9-12900K 處理器，ASRock Z690M-ITX/ax 主機板，Radeon RX 6900 XT OC Formula 16GB 顯示卡，且提供 32GB 記憶體及 2000GB SSD，更於盒上印上 SEGA 及 Sonic 的圖案。在官方的影片中可見，只需將它搭載在遙控車底盤上，便最高可以時速 100 公里在路上奔馳，成為世上最快速的（物理）PC。</p><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_36368"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/vOXQb6A6JWw?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://sega.jp/special/sale/steam/present.html">SEGA 官網</a></p><p>—</p><p><u>unwire.hk </u>Mewe 專頁 : <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><u>https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</u></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
